    .about-content
      %h2.section How does nReduce work?
      .detail
        %h3 We let any startup begin but only great teams will graduate.
        %br
        %h3 We require that each team build and ship product each week.  Groups of teams meet and share feedback / ideas.

      %h2.section What does a week in nReduce look like?
      .detail
        %h3 By Wednesday at noon, each team will need to decide what they will build for the week.  They record what they will build and start to work.  Then by Tuesday at 4pm, they will need to record whether or not they have shipped and demo their new funtionality to their group.
      %h2.section Do we interact in person or online?
      .detail
        %h3 Both, in cities where we have enough teams we have selected a physical location for the teams to meet up and share their progress.  For those who do not have a physical location, teams will sign into our site and interact with other teams online.
      %h2.section How do great teams get in front of investors?
      .detail
        %h3 Graduating teams will have their pitch reviewed by our Investor Judges and be featured in our online demo day.  We are currently building our list of judges, this will be released in coming weeks.

